Package demo.projects.test.framework.helpers.test.data.loader

Class TestDataLoader

java.lang.Object
demo.projects.test.framework.helpers.test.data.loader.TestDataLoader
Direct Known Subclasses:
TestDataLoaderOpenCSV
public abstract class TestDataLoader
extends java.lang.Object
CSV Test data loader.

Loads and parses test data from CSV afterwards loads images for parsed object, if test data object implements an interface extending TestDataWithImages.
